	<!-- Reptile - Bear -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
		<defName>GR_Bearodile</defName>		
		<label>bearodile</label>
		<description>The dinosaur nerds out there should love this hybrid. Got one hell of a nasty bite and even the claws will both knock you down and make you unable to get up. Often bred for hunting by the bored one percenters who want to eat massive drumsticks, caveman style.\n\nA reptile hybrid with recessive ursine genes. Highly intelligent and an exceptional frontline trooper, with a venomous, stunning attack, fast movement speed and high health pool.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Gameplay effect:&lt;/color&gt; All reptile hybrids have good temperature tolerance ranges and venomous attacks.</description>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>4.8</MoveSpeed>
			<ComfyTemperatureMin>-75</ComfyTemperatureMin>
			<ComfyTemperatureMax>75</ComfyTemperatureMax>
			<MarketValue>400</MarketValue>
			<FilthRate>4</FilthRate>
			<MeatAmount>75</MeatAmount>
		</statBases>
		
