	<!-- Reptile - Boomalope -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
		<defName>GR_Boomsnake</defName>
		<label>boomsnake</label>
		<description>What happens when you mix a spitting cobra, a rattlesnake and a creature designed to lactate refined fuel? This abomination, that’s what. Drive it into a corner and it’ll hurt itself to release deadly neurotoxins. Try and keep your distance and it’ll spit toxic blood right at you. Clearly someone was a sore loser in playing pretend games as a child, but had either the brains or the money to prove themselves right.\n\nA reptile hybrid with recessive boomalope genes. Decently intelligent with a nasty bite and even nastier ranged attack, both causing toxic buildup. Quite a high metabolism which supports its various combat abilities, best suited for home defence.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Gameplay effect:&lt;/color&gt; All reptile hybrids have good temperature tolerance ranges and venomous attacks.</description>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>3</MoveSpeed>
			<ComfyTemperatureMin>-75</ComfyTemperatureMin>
			<ComfyTemperatureMax>75</ComfyTemperatureMax>
			<MarketValue>400</MarketValue>
		
		</statBases>
		
